start.body:
Elane kakolkol ko am rej kwalok bwe eor am COVID-19 (ejab jen men ko im rej kein jumae teej) komaron kwalok kin teej eo am ako koban kwalok etam.

Kolak kwalok kin tobrak in test eo am enaj koman bwe ro jet ilo jukjukin bed eo ren kejbarok lok an ajeded kij eo.

verification_code_info.how_do_i_get_body: Kurlok ro ilo jikin ajmour eo, {{healthAuthorityName}}.
verification_code_info.how_do_i_get_header: Ewi wawein ao bok verification code eo?
verification_code_info.info_body:
Verification code ej juon code eo rej lewaj nan kwe jen jikin ajmour eo, {{healthAuthorityName}}, elane tobrak in test eo am ej kwalok ke kobok kij in.

Verification code eo ej jerbal nan kamool ke tobrak in test eo am me kobok kij ie ej lukin mool.

Kajojo verification code enaj jemlok kitien ilo juon ien eo ekadu nan kwalok ke teej ko remaat kitier rejab lilok.

Elane kwonaaj ioon bod elane kwonaaj jilkinlok verification code eo, kwoj aikuij kajjitok kin juon code keel jen ro ilo jikin ajmour mokta jen am bar jilkinlok.
verification_code_info.what_happens_body:
Elane kwonaaj jilkinlok verification code eo, app eo enaj kajjitok bwe kwon jeere nomba eo raar lewaj jen kein jerbal ko am im emoj an konaak ie.

Elane kwonaaj lelok melim, app in enaaj jilkinlok ki kein nan kojjela in kapopo jobor eo. Notification server eo enaaj kejeleik kein jerbal ek am im emoj am konaak ie ikijeen tobrak in test eo am im ej kwalok ke kobok kij in.

App eo ejab ebok ak kejbarok melele ko kin kwe. Ki ko wot emoj keleti im rej bed ilo kein jerbal eo am rej share ie.
verification_code_info.what_happens_header: Ta eo enaaj walok elane inaaj jilkinlok code eo ao?

onboarding.privacy_policy: Kakien ikijeen men ko rej aikuij ittino wot

protect_privacy.body_1: ID kein rejab kwalok kin men ko ikijeen armij im rej oktak aolep 10-20 minit nan kejbarok iok.
protect_privacy.body_2: Talboon rej leto-letak melele ko kin ID ko iben kein jerbal ko jet ilo aer kejerbale Bluetooth Low Energy. Ej kotlok bwe {{applicationName}} nan lale am delon ilo an ittino wot melele ko ikijeem, jekdoon ne kojab kobelloke lo kein jerbal eo nejum.
protect_privacy.body_3: Elikin an teej eo kwalok ke ewor am naninmij in COVID-19, ro rej kojerbale men kein remaron jeere verification code eo ibben {{applicationName}} nan kamoole kein jeek ko. Jabdewot ID lo talboon ko aer rej kokkalle im delon nan server eo. Jerbal in Verification in ej jiban kejbarok jen riabin ripoot ko ikijeen ro rebok kij in.
protect_privacy.body_4: Elane flagged ID eo emaaje ID eo emoj likit ilo talboon eo nejum, menin ej kalikar ke emoj am bed iturin juon eo ewor naninmij in COVID-19 ibben. Enin ej wawein {{applicationName}} ej kwalok elane kwaar ejedmatmat nan kij in.
protect_privacy.body_5:
Elane enaaj maaj, {{applicationName}} renaaj kojjelaik iok im lewaj karok ko nan kwe jen jikin ajmour eo am.

Enin ej wawein {{applicationName}} nan kokkajoor iok nan komman lomnak ko kin ajmour eo am, im kejbarok jukjukin bed eo am, ilo aer jaje kin won kwe ak ia ko kwaar bed ie.
protect_privacy.subheader_1: Elane konaaj kajoe kojjela in kapopo ko, talboon eo am emoj aer taak e ippen ID ko rej ukooktak
protect_privacy.subheader_2: Talbool ko ewor kojjela in kapopo ko im rejo rej jeniji ID ko ibben kein jerbal ko jet rej maron loi
protect_privacy.subheader_3: Elane eo ej kejerbale im teej eo an ebok kij in, remaron kelet nan jeer e naninmej in aer ilo an jab walok etan
protect_privacy.subheader_4: Kajojo talboon rej biin i server eo nan liij in ID ko rekokkalle im kabok aer meej
protect_privacy.subheader_5: Renaaj kojjelaik iok elane {{applicationName}} ej loe juon eo ebok naninmej in im emeeje yuk im ewor bulaak ID

guidance.call_your_healthcare_provider: Kurlok ro rej lorlorjake ajmour, lain eo an ebok naan in kapilok, ak eo lo jikin uno eo ilowaan 24 awa.
guidance.dont_go_to_work: Jab etal nan jerbal, jikuul, ak ijoko elon armej ie.
guidance.dont_use_public_transport: Jab iuwe lo wa ko elon armej rej iuwe ie ak iuwe ibben bar juon.
guidance.drink_water: Idaak elab den im den ko jet rejab kolar nan kajbarok enbwinnum jen an mora (mora enbwin).
guidance.feeling_fine: Emman ad ron ke emman am mour. Kwoj aikuij etale wot kakolkol ko im bed wot mweo.
guidance.find_telehealth: Kabok jikin jiban ko kin ajmour im ta jerbal ko aer
guidance.follow_cdc_guidance: Elane ewor am kakolkol, Lori unin tel ko an CDC.
guidance.if_symptoms_develop: Elane enaaj wor am enjaake in kakolkol in COVID-19 ak elane enaaj nana lok, kurlok ro ilo jikin ajmour eo, jikin takto talbool lain eo, ak jikin ebok uno eo ippen ro rej jerbal ie.
guidance.may_help_you_feel_better: Erkein ej jet bunten ne ko nan kokmanman am mour:
guidance.monitor_your_symptoms: Jolok bod bwe konaninmij. Bed wot mweo im etale kakolkol ko am. Kurlok rikajmour eo elane kakolkol ko rej nana lok, bed wot mweo.
guidance.protect_others: Bok bunten kein nan kejbarok ro jet jen air naninmij.
guidance.seek_medical_care: Elane kwoj kile ke eidin ak enana lok am bed, kebaak jikin takto.
guidance.stay_6_feet_away: Bed 6 ne etolok jen armej ro jet im etolok jen ijoko elon armej ie.
guidance.stay_at_home: Bed wot mweo ijelokin ne kwoj bukot ajmour.
guidance.stay_away_from_higher_risk_people: Elane emaron, bed etolok jen ro me ebidodo aer bok COVID-19.

guidance.take_temperature: Bok bwilim ruo katton ilo juon raan im lale kakolkol ko ikijen COVID-19.

verification_code_alerts.code_used_body: Verification code eo im rar letok emoj an jerbal.
verification_code_alerts.invalid_code_body:
Kamol code eo kwar jilikintok ejab jimwe.

Code eo am ej aikuij juon eo emoj kamole jen jikin ejmour eo im rar lewaj nan kwe.

Emaron bar juon code eo am ejemlok kitien. Kin menin, kwonaj aikuj bar kajitok juon code kaal jen jikin ejmour eo.
verification_code_alerts.network_connection_body: Kwoj aikuij connect nan WiFi nan am jilikin lok verification code.
verification_code_alerts.unknown_body: Ekar walok juon bwod eo im jekar jab kotmene ke emaron walok. Jouij im bar kajeon.
